{"word":"νεοσσεύω","slug":"νεοσσεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>νεοσσεύω</b></el> <el>(νεοσσεύω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:νεοσσός'><el>νεοσσός</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to hatch</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to build a nest</i>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, <el>ὅσα ἦν νενεοσσευμένα ὀρνίθων γένεα</el> as many as <i>had their nests built</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}